lable only after the Investor is registered on the site. <br><b>1.6</b> Actions that may harm the Company's website are considered illegal and will be regarded as fraud and prosecuted under copyright law. <br></div><div class="rules"><h3><b>2.</b>RIGHTS AND OBLIGATIONS OF THE COMPANY</h3><b>2.1</b> The Company is obliged to provide the Investor with the stable work of all the services of the website. <br><b>2.2</b> The Company promises to make payments to the Investor on time depending on the chosen investment plan.<br><b>2.3</b> The Company guarantees the complete confidentiality of all received information from the Investor, except for the cases when the disclosure of this information is necessary to resolve the disputes that have arisen. <br><b>2.4</b> The Company has the right to refuse to register the Investor without explanation.<br><b>2.5</b> The Company does not bear material and other liability to the Investor if he has suffered material damage from third parties through its own fault.<h3><b>3.</b> RIGHTS AND OBLIGATIONS OF THE INVESTOR</h3><b>3.1</b> An obligatory condition for being the Investor of the Company is the Investor's registration on the site. <br><b>3.2</b> During the process of registration the Investor should provide only real data. <br><b>3.3</b> Registration of an account is allowed only if the Investor opens the account using his real name. Registration of an account using names of third-party persons, as well as leading the investment activities from third-party accounts is strictly prohibited.<br><b>3.4</b> Multiple registration of accounts by one Investor is strictly prohibited. <br><b>3.5</b> Input and withdrawal of funds can be made only using accounts that are registered by the Investor. The use of the third-party accounts for financial transactions will be considered by the Company as fraud.<br><b>3.6</b> Violation of any of the clauses of the current Agreement may cause a complete blockage of the Investor's account.<br><b>3.7</b> It is prohibited to use spam technology to introduce other Investors into misconceptions about the Company's activities.<br><b>3.8</b> The Customer has the right to terminate cooperation with the Company without giving reasons.<br><b>3.9</b> If the Investor finds that his account was hacked by third parties, he can contact the support service to restore access to the account.</div><div class="rules"><h3><b>4.</b> SECURITY</h3><b>4.1</b> The Company is obliged to ensure the safety of work and to manage this uses modern security technologies and services.<br><b>4.2</b> The Investor is also obliged to provide security of his perdonal data (login, password, etc.) which are used for investment. The Company recommends that the Investor use a complicated password to access the account. <br><b>4.3</b> The Company is not liable for leak of Investor's personal data (login, password, etc.) to the trird-party due to the fault of the customer.</div><div class="rules"><h3><b>5.</b> PROJECT REGULATIONS</h3><b>5.1</b> Deposits <br><b>5.1.1</b> The deposit body is replenishable, irretrievable and is locked for infinite period of time<br><b>5.1.2</b> Minimal deposit is 1 USD <br><b>5.1.3</b> Regulated profitability is up to 25% per month <br><b>5.1.4</b> We have 3 levels of the partner program. You get a reward from your affiliates (referrals) in such a way:<br>1) Referrals in your first line. You get 3% from every recharge of this partners. Also you get 10% from their income. <br>2) Referrals in your second line. You get 1% from every recharge of this partners. Also you get 4% from their income. Is available when you have 15 or more active referrals.<br>3) Referrals in your third line. You get 1% from every recharge of this partners. Also you get 1% from their income. Is available when you have 15 or more active referrals.<br><b>5.1.5</b> In order to get income from your second and third lines you need to have 15 active referrals in your first line. Then you are to contact the support with a request using Topic "Second and third referral lines request". When your data will be checked successfully the second and the third referral lines will be available to you. <br><b>5.1.6</b>Holidays and days off when the exchanges are closed are non-trading days <br><b>5.1.7</b> Rate decisions and NFP are non-trading days<br><b>5.1.8</b> Profit accrual are carried out on weekdays daily except for non-trading days <br><br><b>5.2</b> Funds input/withdrawal, reinvestment <br><b>5.2.1</b> Deposit of funds: deposits are made through electronic payment systems such as AdvCash and PerfectMoney in instant mode. Funds are charged to the account instantly. <br><b>5.2.2</b> Withdrawal of funds is processed in manual mode. Withdrawal requests are created through the personal office on Sundays from 00:00 MSK till 23:55 MSK. The minimum amount for withdrawal is 10 USD. Payments are processed during the next business week from Monday to Friday.When there are few withdrawal requests the processing of the output takes less than 72 hours, starting from Monday. Otherwise, the withdrawal can be processed until the friday evening. Withdrawal requests created with violation of the rules are canceled, funds are not returned to the account. <br><b>5.2.3</b> Reinvestment of funds is available on Saturdays from 00:00 MSK till 23:55 MSK. How to make reinvestment please refer to the FAQ section. The minimum amount to reinvest is 0 USD. <br><b>5.2.4</b> All operations are checked by operators. In the case of a violation of the rules when withdrawing funds, the following measures will be applied. For the first time, a warning + cancellation of withdrawal without a refund to the balance. The second time, a warning + cancellation of withdrawal without a refund to the balance + freezing of the account for a week. <br><b>5.2.5</b> If the investor violates any of the rules clauses 3 times his account is blocked in the system without a refund forever. <br><br><b>5.3</b> Support. <br><b>5.3.1</b> If you have any questions, write to us through the feedback form in the "Contact us" section. <br><b>5.3.2</b> In the topic of the letter you should write the reason for your request (wishes / technical questions / financial questions and so on). Letters without topics and with topics without meaning (dycee / oaoanomat / "any other abracadabra is not bound with the work of the project" and so on) will be ignored. <br><b>5.3.3</b> Requests are processed within 24 hours. When there is a large number of requests the response time can be increased. <br></div><div class="rules"><h3><b>6.</b> FINAL PROVISIONS</h3><b>6.1</b> This Agreement comes into force from the moment when the Investor is registered on the Company's website. <br><b>6.2</b> The Company has the right to terminate, reduce, modify or expand this Agreement or any service that is the property of the Company. <br><b>6.3</b> It is forbidden to invest funds that were received by the Investor illegally.<br></div></div></div></section><?php echo $_smarty_tpl->getSubTemplate ('footer.tpl', $_smarty_tpl->cache_id, $_smarty_tpl->compile_id, null, null, array(), 0);?>

